Reasoning: The paper deals with the secure transmission of information over a wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of helpers and cooperative jamming also involves networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the use of Gaussian distributions and the optimization of degrees of freedom can be related to machine learning and optimization (cs.MM).
